Homepage: https://github.com/ultrarisc/cpu-ec-reporter/

Package: cpu-ec-reporter
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, lm-sensors, jq, xxd
Description: CPU/EC reporting and RTL8211F LED setup helpers
 Periodically reads CPU temperature and reports it to EC via serial.
 Includes a suspend/resume hook for EC state notifications.
 Provides a systemd one-shot service to initialize RTL8211F LED behavior.
